==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪdəl|-ɪdəl]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# a [[puzzle]], [[mystery]], or other [[problem]] of an [[intellectual]] nature; a mental challenge
# a [[sieve]]

====Synonyms====
*[[enigma]]
*[[conundrum]]
*[[brain-teaser]]

